msgstr "Hochpassfilter"

#: src/ui/views/mic.rs:233
msgid "Cuts low-frequency rumble — AC, wind, mic-stand bumps."
msgstr ""
"Schneidet tieffrequentes Rumpeln ab – Netzbrummen, Wind, Mikrofonständer-"
